==English==

===Etymology===
Taking the name of '''[[w:Rick Santorum|Rick Santorum]]''', a [[senator]] who described homosexual acts as part of a class of deviant sexual behavior, including incest, polygamy, and bestiality. More on the etymology can be found in [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Savage_Love#Santorum Wikipedia]
===Noun===
'''santorum'''
# the frothy mix of [[lube]] and [[fecal]] matter that is sometimes the [[byproduct]] of [[anal sex]]

